    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1899-10-23T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1899-10-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="792"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d792">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Loomis</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-10-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 23, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Wait events. Can not assume to judge conditional title. Test of recognition is
                    complete regency of affairs by de facto government capable of fulfilling
                    international obligations. Meanwhile transact necessary business with locally
                    responsible authorities.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hay.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
